jva-fbxb-jca.title: Onboarding
jva-fbxb-jca.description: Let's discuss the marketing and all.

conversation.speaker: Kevin
conversation.text: I'm doing great. What about you?

conversation.speaker: Nathalie
conversation.text: I'm doing well too. So, what do you want to discuss about Recap?

conversation.speaker: Kevin
conversation.text: I think we should discuss our marketing strategy for the upcoming quarter.

conversation.speaker: Nathalie
conversation.text: That sounds like a good idea. What do you have in mind?

conversation.speaker: Kevin
conversation.text: I was thinking of focusing on social media campaigns and influencer marketing.

conversation.speaker: Nathalie
conversation.text: That's a great idea. We should also look into email marketing and search engine optimization.

conversation.speaker: Kevin
conversation.text: Yes, those are both important strategies. Let's make sure to include them in our plan.

conversation.speaker: Nathalie
conversation.text: Agreed. I'll start working on the plan right away.

conversation.speaker: Kevin
conversation.text: Sounds good. Let's touch base again next week to review it.

conversation.speaker: Nathalie
conversation.text: Will do. Have a good day!
